name: MAINBORI SOCIO-ECONOMIC ORGANISATION FOR RURAL DEVELOPMENT OF ASSAM
briefDescription: our organisation has been working in rural and char areas for the socio-economic development of the poor and needy persons in the field of Education, Health, Environment, Agriculture, Forestation, women empowerment, communication Development and Swatch Bharat Abhiyan etc. This Organisation has been operating for the people and by the people of Assam.
